tags.fixme: Should this really be tagged as bicycle=yes? While bicycles can physically pass, it's probably not legal for bicycles to be ridden over the pavement (though cyclists can dismount and walk across it), and there seem to be no signs permitting cycles.
No bus stop here, though one near the mailbox
